name: Dotfiles
body:
## My collection of config files and scripts.
A pretty eclectic mix of useful scripts and random experimental fun. 

### DISCLAIMER
I don't expect much of this the best way of doing things and am open to any new ideas!

To get started
```
$ git clone https://github.com/mdiluz/dotfiles.git
$ cd dotfiles
$ ./bootstrap.sh
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
